In the first quarter of 2010, the loss of AvtoVAZ amounted to 2.6 billion rubles, in the second quarter, net profit under RAS amounted to 1 billion rubles.[5] AvtoVAZ's sales in the II quarter doubled compared to the I quarter.[5]
Since 2011, after the acquisition of OAG LLC, AvtoVAZ began to take into account the products of the Izhevsk Automobile Plant, which became a subsidiary of the company, in its production indicators. This year, both enterprises produced 593.3 thousand cars. Sales of the plant increased compared to last year by 10.6% - up to 578.3 thousand rubles.